'''Sholto's Shuttles!''' was a travel company, presumably owned by [[Sholto]], which rented out [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|''Lambda''-class T-4a shuttles]] for either day excursions or party bookings. They were known for running a service to an [[Asteroid field/Legends|asteroid belt]].

